snippet.textDisplay: Arnob, you never fail to do justice to Bangladeshi music! You are Bangladesh’s pride and a musical asset! Thank you soo much for Tati! You did Bangladesh proud, you did me proud as a Bangladeshi, you did this precious Bangladeshi tati heritage proud, and you did Coke Studio Bangla proud! Thank you! Your music video was not only a masterpiece like you are, but also a protest and a slap against India’s claim about the Tangail sharee! I loved EVERYTHING about this video! The fusion, the music, the inclusion of the original singer, Jaya Ahsan, Oli boy, the showcasing of the taat process, the beautiful, vibrant colored studio…my goodness! It’s not just an audio feast but a visual feast!😍❤️ You’re a very talented, humble musician, singer! ❤️❤️
